title: OnePlus 10 Pro finally launches globally with OxygenOS 12.1; Bullets Wireless Z2 and Radiant Silver Buds Pro tag along
content:

description: The OnePlus 10 Pro has been launched globally with OxygenOS 12.1 in tow, along with flagship specifications such as a Snapdragon 8 Gen 1.
